#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/config.phtml:101
msgid ""
"Whether the married name (from a \"MARRIED\" or \"_MARNM\" name entry) is "
"shown — replacing the birth name, appended in brackets after the birth name, "
"or hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ali se prikaže poročno ime (iz zapisa NAME tipa \"MARRIED\" ali \"_MARNM\") "
"— namesto rojstnega imena, dodano v oklepajih za rojstnim imenom ali "
"skrito.Ali je poročni priimek (iz vnosa imena vrste \"MARRIED\" ali "
"\"_MARNM\") prikazan — namesto rojstnega imena, dodan v oklepaju za rojstnim "
"imenom ali skrit."

